=form_for('pdfs', :html => {:multipart => true}) do |f|
  
  =f.label t('pdf.post')
  =f.file_field "pdf"
  .actions
    = f.submit I18n.t('submit')

%p.blurb
  This site will remove encryption as well as restrictions on copy/paste and printing from PDF files. We do not keep any of the files you upload. Ever.
